  %p
    The Grove - Buzzer module has a piezo buzzer as the main component. The piezo can
    be connected to digital outputs, and will emit a tone when the output is HIGH. Alternatively,
    it can be connected to an analog pulse-width modulation output to generate various tones and effects.

